Package it.polimi.ingsw.model

Class Tile

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.model.Tile
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable
public class Tile
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable, java.io.Serializable
The tile is the fundamental component of the IslandBoard. It's these objects that keep the state of the IslandBoard in memory. On a tile it is allowed to build a tower and place a worker. If there is a worker or a dome on the tile, it's occupied.
See Also:
Cloneable, Serializable, Tile.IndexTile, Tile.Building, Worker, Serialized Form
